        What Happens on Auction Day in Brisbane: a Complete Seller's Guide
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Auction day is fast and unfamiliar if you have not been through it before. Here is a step-by-step account of what to expect, from the night before to the moment the hammer falls.
      </p>
